   <TEXT>
   <S PAR='1' RSNT='1' SNO='1'>Subject One Hundred Ninety THE NECESSITY OF BELIEVING THAT GOD IS Scripture: Heb 11:6 God is The creation of the universe proves that God is.</S>
   <S PAR='2' RSNT='1' SNO='2'>The order of the universe proves that God is.</S>
   <S PAR='3' RSNT='1' SNO='3'>Man s physical body and mentality prove that God is.</S>
   <S PAR='4' RSNT='1' SNO='4'>God is hidden Although God exists, He is hidden.</S>
   <S PAR='5' RSNT='1' SNO='5'>Because God is Spirit, He is hidden to materialistic man.</S>
   <S PAR='6' RSNT='1' SNO='6'>As a result, the materialistic man cannot see or touch the Spirit.</S>
   <S PAR='7' RSNT='1' SNO='7'>God s honor, greatness, and holiness cause Him to hide Himself from man who is low and filthy.</S>
   <S PAR='8' RSNT='1' SNO='8'>You must believe that God is You must believe because God is hidden.</S>
   <S PAR='9' RSNT='1' SNO='9'>You must believe because God is Spirit and cannot be seen by man s naked eye.</S>
   <S PAR='10' RSNT='1' SNO='10'>You must believe because God is honorable holy, and we are low and filthy.</S>
   <S PAR='11' RSNT='1' SNO='11'>Thus for man to touch God, there is no way other than the way of believing.</S>
   <S PAR='12' RSNT='1' SNO='12'>The results of believing in God By believing in God you receive His life.</S>
   <S PAR='13' RSNT='1' SNO='13'>Believing in God causes you to have the sensation of being enlightened within.</S>
   <S PAR='14' RSNT='1' SNO='14'>Through your believing you become well-pleasing to God.</S>
   <S PAR='15' RSNT='1' SNO='15'>How to believe Confess that you are a sinner before God.</S>
   <S PAR='16' RSNT='1' SNO='16'>Repent and come forward to God, believing that He is.</S>
   </TEXT>
